query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(a1 b q1 s t1 tq1 u1) NoHashJoin(a1 b q1 s t1 tq1 u1 acc) */ select count(*)
from question AS q1
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.favorite_count >= 0 AND q1.favorite_count <= 10000
inner join tag AS t1
on t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('16.04',
'divisibility',
'grub2',
'linear-algebra',
'manifolds',
'ring-theory')
inner join answer AS a1
on q1.id = a1.question_id
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND s.site_id = a1.site_id AND s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('askubuntu',
'math')
inner join badge AS b
on s.site_id = b.site_id AND b.name IN ('Autobiographer',
'Caucus',
'Critic',
'Custodian',
'Editor',
'Necromancer',
'Nice Answer',
'Notable Question',
'Promoter',
'Revival',
'Scholar',
'Student',
'Tumbleweed',
'Yearling')
inner join so_user AS u1
on s.site_id = u1.site_id AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND b.user_id = u1.id AND u1.upvotes >= 0 AND u1.upvotes <= 100
inner join account AS acc
on acc.id = u1.account_id;
